PROMPT italian_neorealism_analysis
WITH BUDGET 6000 tokens
USING MODEL "claude-sonnet-4-5"

SELECT
    system_role("You are a film history expert specializing in Italian cinema and post-war European film movements with deep knowledge of neorealism theory and practice.")

GENERATE
    analyze_movement("Explain Italian Neorealism as a film movement, covering: the historical context and origins of neorealism in post-WWII Italy, its core defining characteristics including use of non-professional actors, location shooting, social realism themes, documentary-style cinematography, and focus on working-class struggles, and provide two landmark films of the movement with their directors, explaining why each film is considered essential to neorealism and how it exemplifies the movement's key principles.")
WITH OUTPUT BUDGET 2000 tokens, TEMPERATURE 0.2, FORMAT markdown;